            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">登徒子好色賦不得不讀，成了宋玉的腦殘粉。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1022220011">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1022220011" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1022220011" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1022220011">有用</a>
